<MainLayout title="About Auto Video">
  <h1>About Auto Video</h1>
  <section class="panel">
    <p>
      Auto Video is designed for teams that need to ship video ideas quickly. We combine prompt engineering and AI orchestration to propose complete video structures, scripts, and visual concepts—all in minutes.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our platform streamlines the entire video creation process: from idea conception to final export. Whether you're creating marketing videos, product explainers, or social content, Auto Video helps teams produce professional videos faster than traditional workflows.
    </p>
    <p>
      We believe in removing friction from creative production. No login required, no complex setup—just describe your vision and let AI handle the heavy lifting.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
